These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: azure, purple, amber, fuchsia, black, emerald, yellow
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: july, august, april, march, september, june, february
 1. the person who likes azure is between the person who likes fuchsia and the person who likes yellow##2
 2. the person who likes purple is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 4. the person who likes black is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in september##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
 9. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
10. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
11. the person who likes emerald is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Color   | fuchsia | azure | yellow | purple    | amber | black   | emerald    |
| Birthday         | june  | august   | march | july | april   | february | september |

