.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: singing, cooking, traveling, filmmaking, board-games, hiking, camping
There are 7 different favourite beverages: lemonade, sprite, mirinda, fanta, coffee, iced-tea, almond-milk
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person drinking iced-tea##2
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is in the middle##1
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
8. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby          | board-games | traveling | hiking | cooking | camping | singing      | filmmaking  |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | fanta  | almond-milk     | mirinda     | coffee  | lemonade | sprite |

