.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: aconite, tulip, marigold, daisy, bellflower, balloon-flower, dahlia
There are 7 different favourite colors: white, lilac, red, coral, amber, lavender, blue
 1. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
 2. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
 3. the person who likes amber is the person who growsdahlia##1
 4. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 5. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 6. the person who growsdaisy is the person who likes coral##1
 7. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who likes red##1
 8. the person who likes white is between the person who likes blue and the person who growsdaisy##2
 9. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
10. the person who growstulip is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Flower   | dahlia | bellflower | aconite | tulip   | daisy | marigold | balloon-flower |
| Color           | amber | lavender     | lilac     | red | coral   | white   | blue    |

