.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: western, crime, satire, family, disaster, action, comedy
City: venice, san-francisco, edinburgh, colone, london, marseilles, hannover
 1. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 2. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 4. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 5. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 6. the person traveling to colone is between the person watching satire movies and the person traveling to marseilles##2
 7. the person watching western movies is in the middle##1
 8. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 9. the person watching crime movies is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
10. the person traveling to venice is the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Movie-Genre      | satire    | disaster  | family  | western  | comedy      | action       | crime |
| City   | london | colone | marseilles | hannover | venice | edinburgh | san-francisco  |

