.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: blue, mauve, purple, fuchsia, ivory, aquamarine, yellow
7 different pets are kept: hedgehog, frog, chinchilla, dog, pony, rabbit, cat
1. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
2. the owner of the pony is the person who likes mauve##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person who likes yellow and the person who likes blue##2
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is in the middle##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
8. the owner of the frog is the person who likes fuchsia##1
9. the person who likes ivory is the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Color   | fuchsia      | ivory | blue | purple | yellow      | mauve      | aquamarine |
| Pet     | frog | rabbit | cat       | hedgehog | chinchilla | pony | dog |

