.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, lemonade, water, mirinda, tea, hot-chocolate
The people use 7 different means of transport: roller, train, bus, car, trike, skateboard, motorbike
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person driving the bus is the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is between the person driving the trike and the person drinking milk##2
7. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the train##1
8. the person drinking tea is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Beverage     | mirinda | milk | water | tea | iced-tea | lemonade     | hot-chocolate |
| Transport   | bus   | car    | motorbike    | trike      | train  | roller | skateboard |

