.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There 7 different types of food: pepper, peach, watermelon, strawberry, pineapple, apple, eggplant
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: hip-hop, indie, jazz, electronic, punk, blues, soul
 1. the fan blues is the person eating pineapple##1
 2. the person eating peach is on the left of the fan soul##1
 3. the fan indie is in the middle##1
 4. the person eating watermelon is between the fan punk and the fan soul##2
 5. the fan hip-hop is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
 6. the person eating pepper is on the left of the fan hip-hop##1
 7. the fan electronic is the person eating pepper##1
 8. the person eating apple is the fan punk##1
 9. the fan jazz is between the fan punk and the person eating pineapple##2
10. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Food   | pepper | peach    | strawberry | watermelon   | apple | eggplant    | pineapple |
| Music-Genre      | electronic | hip-hop | soul    | indie | punk    | jazz | blues  |

