 1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
 4. the tower house is on the left of the cottage house##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the tower house##1
 6. the ranch-style house is between the farmhouse house and the cottage house##2
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the cottage house##1
 9. the tower house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
10. the tower house is between the cottage house and the gothic-revival house##2
11. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
